  "privacy": {
    "title": "Privacy Policy",
    "s1_title": "1. Data Controller",
    "s1_text": "Responsible for the processing of personal data within this support portal is S. Merken, Z-Evolutions, operator of z-evolutions.de. Contact: support@z-evolutions.de",
    "s2_title": "2. What Data We Process",
    "s2_text": "As part of your support request, we process the following data: first name, last name, email address, and the content of your request (subject and description). This data is required to process your request.",
    "s3_title": "3. Purpose and Legal Basis",
    "s3_text": "Your data will be used exclusively to process your support request. The legal basis is Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b GDPR (performance of a contract) as well as your explicit consent pursuant to Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR.",
    "s4_title": "4. Storage Period",
    "s4_text": "Your data will be stored as long as your support process is active. Activity logs (audit log) are automatically deleted after 90 days. Upon request, your data will be anonymized in accordance with Art. 17 GDPR.",
    "s5_title": "5. Your Rights",
    "s5_text": "You have the right to access, rectification, erasure, and restriction of processing of your data (Art. 15–18 GDPR) as well as the right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR). Self-deletion of your account is possible directly in the portal.",
    "s6_title": "6. Technical Information",
    "s6_text": "This system uses exclusively technically necessary storage mechanisms (localStorage) for session data, theme, and language settings. No tracking cookies are set, no external services are integrated, and no data is passed on to third parties. Fonts are provided locally — there is no contact with Google servers.",
    "close_btn": "Understood",
    "link": "Privacy Policy",
    "checkbox": "I have read the <1>Privacy Policy</1> and agree to the processing of my data to handle my support request.",
    "checkbox_required": "Please agree to the privacy policy to proceed.",
    "checkbox_before": "I have read the",
    "checkbox_after": "and agree to the processing of my data to handle my support request.",
    "s7_title": "7. Contact & Withdrawal",
    "s7_text": "For questions about data protection or exercising your rights: support@z-evolutions.de — you can withdraw your consent at any time with effect for the future.",
    "imprint_title": "Legal Notice",
    "imprint_link": "Legal Notice",
    "imprint_close": "Close",
    "load_error": "Content could not be loaded.",
    "loading": "Loading…"
